OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FVarying amounts of cloud, this
OL,6,Fperhaps thick enough to produce a very
OL,7,Fisolated light shower. Still bright or
OL,8,Fsunny spells will occur, and most
OL,9,Fplaces will be dry and warm with light
OL,10,Fwinds, these onshore along the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry with patchy cloud and
OL,13,Fclear periods, along with very light
OL,14,Fwinds. There is a chance of a little
OL,15,Fpatchy mist forming late tonight in
OL,16,Frural areas.
OL,17,
OL,18,CFriday:FDry with patchy cloud and
OL,19,Fsunny spells. Despite becoming rather
OL,20,Fbreezy it will be a warm day
OL,21,Feverywhere.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
