OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,6,Fand bright Saturday, warm or very
OL,7,Fwarm. Sunday sunny intervals and
OL,8,Fscattered showers, and feeling
OL,9,Fnoticeably cooler. Monday generally
OL,10,Fdry, with bright or sunny spells and
OL,11,Faverage temperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
